{"tid":1998744,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"黃偉文《傾城》原稿出土　「1997年寫了這一首，大概也不是無緣無故的」","createTime":"2020-05-02T15:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T18:13:44.000Z","uid":41998,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d2e4866d2f0cc39de74b12803a02e8f4d0b90f","tid":1998744,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFyXBLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFyXBLg.png&h=df02de71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉靄瑤 2020/5/2 &mdash; 12:29<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n填詞人黃偉文於instagram一連串發佈了好幾首手寫歌詞原稿，最受網民熱議應是《傾城》，原唱為許美靜。黃偉文寫道：「1997年寫了這一首，大概也不是無緣無故的。現在出土這個版本才是我的原意，出街的那個錄音則是在沒有通知我的情況下的『無故被閹版』，沒辦法，當年是新人，遇到這種事情即使大聲抗議也沒有人除底耳筒傾聽。」細閱原詞更顯黃偉文用心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TFT9XOEbvK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTFT9XOEbvK0&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=6967a139\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TFT9XOEbvK0</a><br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%BB%83%E5%81%89%E6%96%87-%E5%82%BE%E5%9F%8E-%E5%8E%9F%E7%A8%BF%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F-1997%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%AB%E4%BA%86%E9%80%99%E4%B8%80%E9%A6%96-%E5%A4%A7%E6%A6%82%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%A3%E7%84%A1%E6%95%85%E7%9A%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%259F%258E-%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%25A8%25BF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%259C%259F-1997%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E4%25BA%2586%25E9%2580%2599%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25A6%2596-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A6%2582%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2585%25E7%259A%2584%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=09625df3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%2581%2589%25E6%2596%2587-%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%259F%258E-%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%25A8%25BF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%259C%259F-1997%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E4%25BA%2586%25E9%2580%2599%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25A6%2596-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A6%2582%25E4%25B9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2595%2585%25E7%259A%2584%2F&h=0670d4c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E9%BB%83%E5%81%89%E6%96%87-%E5%82%BE%E5%9F%8E-%E5%8E%9F%E7%A8%BF%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%9F-1997%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%AB%E4%BA%86%E9%80%99%E4%B8%80%E9%A6%96-%E5%A4%A7%E6%A6%82%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%A3%E7%84%A1%E6%95%85%E7%9A%84/</a>"},{"pid":"3520310e12bfc0f64be4257d1e8eaf07a2984409","tid":1998744,"uid":12628,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"紅眼睛幽幽的看著這獨城，如同苦笑劑出的高興<br />\n好彩呢個原句無改"},{"pid":"59ffc0b38a31508e0871ec1d32b399372189573d","tid":1998744,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"其實一直都覺得係講香港<br />\n97年喎大佬 其實就算被改 啲歌詞都好明顯"},{"pid":"1becfded5279572990534b3b6da0c4fed711ed6a","tid":1998744,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3520310e12bfc0f64be4257d1e8eaf07a2984409","tid":1998744,"uid":12628,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"紅眼睛幽幽的看著這獨城，如同苦笑劑出的高興<br />\n好彩呢個原句無改"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"*孤"},{"pid":"598621f893b959a0d37f869ce3e6d97445a930aa","tid":1998744,"uid":41998,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:33:03.000Z","msg":"1997年黃偉文寫下的［傾城］ <br />\n2020年公開的原稿歌詞 <br />\n非常鐘愛的一首舊歌 <br />\n太喜歡所以拿來翻唱 <br />\n而上天還給了一個好天氣<br />\n 讓窗外這座城 今天顯得格外令人傾心<br />\n<br />\n傅佩嘉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/fufuamulet?igshid=hmi4d2u2mtu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffufuamulet%3Figshid%3Dhm